# Josep Bernad: Full reference

> Josep Bernad is a house music DJ, multi-instrumentalist, and software engineer from Mallorca, Spain, based in Barcelona. He produces original house music and performs three live formats: a Live Set with live instruments, a House DJ Set, and a Party Set (Open Format).

This file is the long-form companion to `/llms.txt`. It contains the full bios, full FAQs, and live event listings in all three site languages, and is intended for AI assistants and answer engines that want depth beyond the short summary.

